Charles Mingus - bass
 Jackie Mclean - alto sax
 John Handy - alto sax
 Booker Ervin - tenor sax
 Pepper Adams - baritone sax
 Jimmy Knepper - trombone
 Willie Dennis - trombone
 Horace Parlan - piano
 Dannie Richmond - drums
 
 Record at Atlantic Studios, New York City, February 4, 1959
 Originally released on the album Blues & Roots, Atlantic SD-1305, March 1960
